name: should_be_able_to_add_additional_todo_items

testSteps.description: Starts with a todo list containing: {Walk the dog,Put out the garbage}

children.description: Adds todo items called: {Walk the dog,Put out the garbage}
Adds a todo item called: Walk the dog
Adds a todo item called: Put out the garbage

testSteps.description: Adds a todo item called: Buy some milk
Should see that displayed items contain: {Walk the dog,Put out the garbage,Buy some cheese}

exception.message:
Expected: (a collection containing "Walk the dog" and a collection containing "Put out the garbage" and a collection containing "Buy some cheese")
     but: a collection containing "Buy some cheese" was "Buy some milk", was "Walk the dog", was "Put out the garbage", was "Buy some milk"
